Author: J. Jeffery Stager Jr.

LIBWINDOW

  This is a basic wrapper around native OS window APIs. It provids a simple API
  for creating a window for graphics programming

DEPENDENCIES

  This library depends on the following libraries:

    * https://github.com/jefftime/sized_types

USAGE

  To use this library, download the dependencies and add them to your
  CMakeLists.txt with the following lines:

    add_subdirectory("/path/to/sized_types")
    add_subdirectory("/path/to/window")

  After that, link `window` along with the rest of your project's libraries in
  CMake
